Class FullTime

java.lang.Object
Employee
FullTime
Direct Known Subclasses:
Management
public class FullTime
extends Employee
A sub-class of the Employee class that shares the same information, such as profile and payment with the addition of salary that is unique to FullTime and its subclass. We take in a Profile and salary that will be saved to the respective instance variables
Author:
Ashish Shenoy, Abimanyu Ananthu
